	<td><span class="topic">Why aren't more homebrew games sold as ROM only?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17530">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17530</a></span></td>
